  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459890/extras/7d34354401777b863880246a6f7728cc.avif?t=1738662601\" width=620 height=106 /></span><br><br>Robert is the main character of the game. He is a recluse who lives in the middle of a big city. The reason why he became a recluse is a severe migraine that occurs when he sees girls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459890/extras/d39f4d8e419236e8a76531e1e25a09b3.avif?t=1738662601\" width=620 height=106 /></span><br>Cold Harvest is a visual novel with a unique play experience.<br><br>• free movement around the city<br>• interaction with characters and objects<br>• the change of night and day<br>• transfer of objects between locations and their collection<br>• solving riddles and puzzles<br>• dynamically developing plot<br>• mini games built into the gameplay<br>• romantic relationships with many girls<br>• horror and action scenes",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459890/extras/7d34354401777b863880246a6f7728cc.avif?t=1738662601\" width=620 height=106 /></span><br><br>Robert is the main character of the game. He is a recluse who lives in the middle of a big city. The reason why he became a recluse is a severe migraine that occurs when he sees girls.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1459890/extras/d39f4d8e419236e8a76531e1e25a09b3.avif?t=1738662601\" width=620 height=106 /></span><br>Cold Harvest is a visual novel with a unique play experience.<br><br>• free movement around the city<br>• interaction with characters and objects<br>• the change of night and day<br>• transfer of objects between locations and their collection<br>• solving riddles and puzzles<br>• dynamically developing plot<br>• mini games built into the gameplay<br>• romantic relationships with many girls<br>• horror and action scenes",
